data.description: ASSUMABLE LOAN with a 4% INTEREST RATE IF APPROVED! Spacious like new 4 bedroom 2 bathroom home that features an open concept that is neutral, light, bright and spotless. A Large Chef's kitchen with quartz countertops, huge island, stainless steel appliances and gas cooking! The luxurious owner's retreat features an ensuite bath with dual sinks, oversized shower with bench and large walk in closet. You will love the wood look tile throughout the living spaces and baths. The utility room has plenty of storage and room for a 2nd fridge. Upgrades include - Front exterior coach lights, tankless water heater, sprinkler system, doorbell camera, covered back patio and fresh landscaping. Located in highly sought after Northwest ISD and in close proximity to 114, I35W, Alliance, Speedway, dining and shopping. Refrigerator, Washer and Dryer are INCLUDED!
